articles.title: Barry Newman - best known for his roles in Vanishing Point and Petrocelli - dies at 92 - Daily Mail
articles.description: The Boston-born entertainer, best known for his role as Kowalski in the 1971 crime thriller Vanishing Point, passed away May 11.
articles.content:
Actor Barry Newman has died at the age of 92 at New York-Presbyterian Columbia University Irving Medical Center in New York City.
